video.title: Busted!
video.synopsis: Tackling different mysteries in each episode of this game show, seven sleuths get closer to solving the biggest one of all: What happened to Project D?

episodes.synopsis: A man named "M" invites seven people to a murder game party. Among the eight in the room, one will become a victim, and another the culprit.
episodes.title: Forewarned Murder

episodes.synopsis: Recognized for their performance, the detectives report to Jeju Island, where their first client asks them to participate in a treasure hunt.
episodes.title: Treasure Island

episodes.synopsis: While enjoying their break on Jeju Island, the detectives get a shocking call from K, who says Kwang-soo is a prime murder suspect and is on the run.
episodes.title: Kwang-soo, a Murderer

episodes.synopsis: Jong-min comes across a diary of a dead teen girl who was possibly murdered. To find the truth, he gathers the detectives at the school she attended.
episodes.title: Messages from the Dead

episodes.synopsis: A woman turns up dead on an island off the coast of Incheon. The detectives learn that a centuries-old legend of a vampire has haunted the islanders.
episodes.title: The Last Vampire

episodes.synopsis: To find the missing self-portrait of a recently deceased painter, two rival curators at a Seoul art museum each commission a team of detectives.
episodes.title: Battle of the Detectives

episodes.synopsis: Without any cases to solve, the detectives enjoy watching a magic show rehearsal -- until the show's star magician suddenly disappears without a trace.
episodes.title: The Vanished Magician

episodes.synopsis: A man who introduces himself as K's old friend offers the detectives lavish pay and a chance to partake in a special mission -- but there's a catch.
episodes.title: The Mysterious Gentleman

episodes.synopsis: A culprit asks specifically for the detectives to escort him to the police station. In exchange, he promises to tell them everything they want to know.
episodes.title: Operation: Criminal Transport

episodes.synopsis: The detectives receive a text message from K that was written three months ago. It asks them to come to Incheon, where their final test awaits.
episodes.title: The Disappearance of K

episodes.synopsis: Trapped in individual rooms filled with a variety of challenges, each detective tries to figure out how to escape.
episodes.title: Hell of the Gods: Tartarus

episodes.synopsis: The search for K's killer gets complicated when a series of dead bodies are found -- all with a mysterious QR code on them.
episodes.title: Serial Killing

episodes.synopsis: Hired by a client whose family jewels are in danger of being stolen by a nefarious thief, the detectives hurry to get to it first.
episodes.title: Odd Eye: Detective Team vs Phantom Thief

episodes.synopsis: When a shaman needs help finding the scattered numbers of a winning lottery ticket, the detectives race against another team for a big reward.
episodes.title: Along with the Gods; The Return of the Genius Detective Team

episodes.synopsis: The team welcomes a new intern, who leads them to a grisly case involving a divorced couple, their son, and a suspicious neighbor who lives next door.
episodes.title: There Lives a Devil

episodes.synopsis: While investigating a suicide, the detectives go to a spooky village, where mysterious things happen to young women -- and outsiders are not welcome.
episodes.title: The Curse of the Shaman

episodes.synopsis: The detectives split up when they're hired by three estranged brothers of a chaebol family -- all eager to find their late father's will.
episodes.title: The Chairman's Secret

episodes.synopsis: The detectives have fun participating in a crime game show with a K-pop group -- until things get too real.
episodes.title: The Two Clients: The Guys' and Girls' Case Records

episodes.synopsis: Eager for more information about the Flower Killer, the team attends an event, where the detectives come across an unexpected death.
episodes.title: The 5 Flower Killers

episodes.synopsis: Hot on the Flower Killer's trail, the detectives follow a maze of clues from his home to his secret lair, where they learn a shocking truth.
episodes.title: The Flower Of Death

episodes.synopsis: Kwang-soo is back! When a client asks the detectives to uncover which of his roommates is stealing his food, they enter a house filled with secrets.
episodes.title: Share House Food Lupin

episodes.synopsis: The team splits up to take on two cases: one involving a missing professor, and the other a gory murder inside an illegal gambling den.
episodes.title:
Detectives Reunited;
Two New Cases

episodes.synopsis: Investigating the disappearance of a woman's corpse from the morgue, the sleuths encounter a deadly operation with disturbing plans.
episodes.title: The Missing Body

episodes.synopsis: With three women claiming to be his rightful fiancée, a wealthy heir calls on the detectives to deduce which he should marry.
episodes.title: Nam Uk-gun And Seonnyeo

episodes.synopsis: Following clues from a chilling message and a mysterious USB drive, the team races against time to save a hostage from being killed.
episodes.title: Hostage; The Live

episodes.synopsis: After receiving a strange letter from a dead man, the detectives look for answers in his hometown — and from his four suspicious friends.
episodes.title: I Just Died

episodes.synopsis: A client in need of finding a lost boyfriend contacts the team for help, but they're not the only squad of private eyes who show up to take the case.
episodes.title:
The Ghost Client;
The Case of the Imposter Detectives

episodes.synopsis: As the team discovers the truths behind a mysterious organization, they question whether one of their very own could be hiding a dark identity.
episodes.title: The Scale of Destiny
